


	server_tcp.c ----its a server program ,in which it will handle single client at a time.

			compilation... gcc server_tcp.c -o server_tcp
			running....... ./server_tcp 127.0.0.1:8080



	client_tcp.c ----its client program ,in which client code is written.

			compilation... gcc client_tcp.c -o client_tcp
			running....... ./client_tcp.c 127.0.0.1:8080
			 
